<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1041150>
    dc:description "FIGURES 228 – 232. Hydraena species, female gonocoxites, spermathecae, antenna and maxillary palpus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1041150/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1041202>
    dc:description "FIGURES 344 – 345. 344. Modified basal portion of DNA sequence data phylogeny of Hydraena, showing identity of Madagascar species, and new subgenera. Used by permission of Ignacio Ribera. 345. Three examples of aedeagi having very short parameres that originate near the basal orifice, and have only one or two setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1041202/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

